race.comment: SKEDADDLE ARLO (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 6 last run (22.68) at Bulli. Has won three of five starts from this draw. Racing well and deserves a win. TAW GALAXY (4) goes very well here including two wins. Recorded a half a length win (29.69) in a Grade 5 last time at Wentworth Park. Can feature with the right run. AUSSIE'S QUEEN (5) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (30.59) in a Grade 4/5 at Wentworth Park. Is yet to taste defeat at this course and distance. Cannot be taken lightly. DESTROYING (2) clocked an excellent 24.70 win last time. Not to be underestimated.
